linux (4.13.1-1~exp1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release: https://kernelnewbies.org/Linux_4.13
  * New upstream stable update:
    https://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v4.x/ChangeLog-4.13.1

  [ Roger Shimizu ]
