      vmw_gb_surface_define_ioctl() (CVE-2017-7346)
    - [x86] drm/vmwgfx: Make sure backup_handle is always valid (CVE-2017-9605)
    - ALSA: timer: Fix race between read and ioctl (CVE-2017-1000380)
