    - [mips*el/loongson-3] c-r4k: Fix Loongson-3's vcache/scache waysize
      calculation
    - mm/mempolicy.c: fix error handling in set_mempolicy and mbind
      (CVE-2017-7616)
    - random: use chacha20 for get_random_int/long
