    to modules
  * PCI: Enable PCIE_DPC (except for armel/versatile)
  * [amd64] PCI: Enable PCI_HYPERV as module
  * inet: Enable INET_DIAG_DESTROY
  * tcp: Enable TCP_CONG_NV as module
